      • WeblogicMetricCollector

        public WeblogicMetricCollector(java.lang.String hostname,
                               java.lang.String hostPort,
                               java.lang.String user,
                               java.lang.String password)
        Constructs a WeblogicMetricCollector using given parameters. This object provides a unique, immutable, connection.
        Parameters:
        hostname - The hostname of the Weblogic server to connect, using JMX protocol
        hostPort - The port of the Weblogic server to connect, using JMX protocol
        user - The user of the Weblogic server to connect, using JMX protocol (must have proper access rights)
        password - The password of the Weblogic server to connect, using JMX protocol
